title: Dakine Women's Mission Pack
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2013 Womens Mission pack in our Highland print.
Mission Features:
- Vertical board carry straps
- Fleece lined goggle pocket
- Organizer pocket
- Fleece lined sunglass pocket
- Padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15" laptops
- Padded waist belt
